{"tid":1107102,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想請問變頻冷氣機","createTime":"2019-04-15T04:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T02:13:34.000Z","uid":195438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5c70c9b3e45d09d07bf113671220b1d0c7bd4f","tid":1107102,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"屋企有部冷氣，雖然有得較溫度，但根本只係部壓縮機開下停下，開嗰陣好凍，停嗰陣就好焗，咁應該係定頻機啦？<br />\n最近想換機，請問變頻係咪唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如較佢22度就真係22度，唔會開開停停"},{"pid":"c0442f9fadf93a3e374ad2226b5153e3c3b31b07","tid":1107102,"uid":43369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"係 溫度準好多"},{"pid":"ee1d72d258403bf0860e8e6a84e3033ea84799bc","tid":1107102,"uid":49588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"變頻機控制溫度準D，但多D零件，雖則不一定會壞，只是多隻香爐多隻鬼。<br />\n定頻機個壓縮機要不停開下，停下來控制溫度，無噉準，所以成日覺得時凍時熱。機價都平幾舊。<br />\n<br />\n看你個人需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比我選，噉係變頻機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9deffc7d2808689a7edfa6997881c59adf85f77e","tid":1107102,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"有無窗口式變頻機？"},{"pid":"2dfb7ad27c61b76ba5c43193090aefa7cddf25c6","tid":1107102,"uid":34145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9deffc7d2808689a7edfa6997881c59adf85f77e","tid":1107102,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"有無窗口式變頻機？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"有 pan記有 幾款<br />\n窗口變頻 極少款<br />\n基本上pan 記 ko 哂個市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4babaeaed7e32ad01a178c04c715b486bf9ec4f","tid":1107102,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2dfb7ad27c61b76ba5c43193090aefa7cddf25c6","tid":1107102,"uid":34145,"lik